rating_comment:
Hello, at first I want to thank host's brother for being nice to us.Host gave us different location instead of the one we booked. and they didn't tell us anything about the location until I asked them about the address they sent me before check in. It was 12 hours before the check in. My family was very upset. Host told me about their problems which they could tell me earlier.Flat was nice and specious.First 2 days one AC was broken and 3rd day at night they replaced it. Building has some stupid rules which I wasn't aware of .I hope the host will mention everything before they confirm someone's booking. Overall the flat is nice for vacation. Only thing host needs to be more clear and specific.
Thank you

rating_comment: Always it was excellent communication with the host and local contacts. During our stay we felt like our home. Nice, quiet and secured apartment with full of privacy.
